<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TIM15">
<l>nīniṉṟu tāṉavar māmatiṉ mūṉṟu nirantuṭaṉē</l>
<l>tīniṉṟu vēvac cilaitoṭṭa vāṟeṉ ṟiraṅkuvalvāyp</l>
<l>pēyniṉṟu pāṭap peruṅkā ṭaraṅkāp peyarntunaṭṭam</l>
<l>pōyniṉṟu pūtan toḻacceyyu moykaḻaṟ puṇṇiyaṉē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Why the way you stood [and] discharged the bow so that fire constantly burned</l>
<l>as soon it spread in the three great fortresses of the Dānava, meritorious one</l>
<l>with enclosing anklets who, while the Bhūta constantly worship, goes and makes</l>
<l>a dance, moving with the big cremation ground as a stage while demonesses with withered strong mouths sing?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
